OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777050358
OL,3,CFamily left 'empty' after baby's death
OL,4,Cin suspected dog attack
OL,6,FThe family of a three-month-old girl
OL,7,Fwho died after a suspected dog attack
OL,8,Fsay they have been "robbed of a
OL,9,Fbeautiful lifetime" with her.
OL,11,FMaggie-May Ann Moody died at James
OL,12,FCook University Hospital in
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough after an incident at a
OL,14,Fhouse in Hardale Grove, Dormanstown,
OL,15,FRedcar, on Thursday 9 April.
OL,17,FAn inquest, opened at Teesside
OL,18,FCoroner's Court, heard Cleveland
OL,19,FPolice found her after responding to
OL,20,Freports of a dog attack.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
