FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777050358
OL,3,CFamily left 'empty' after baby's death
OL,4,Cin suspected dog attack
OL,6,FThe provisional cause of death was a
OL,7,Fhead injury.
OL,9,FIn a statement Maggie's family said
OL,10,Fshe "changed us in so many ways".
OL,12,FThey added: "She was everything to us.
OL,13,FShe gave us meaning and purpose every
OL,14,Fday and we feel empty.
OL,16,F"As parents and a family, we have been
OL,17,Frobbed of a beautiful lifetime and
OL,18,Fmemories with her.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777050358
OL,3,CFamily left 'empty' after baby's death
OL,4,Cin suspected dog attack
OL,6,F"As a family we were all present with
OL,7,FMaggie at the hospital, and we never
OL,8,Fleft her side.
OL,10,F"Her brother and sister adored little
OL,11,FMaggie and will miss her dearly, as
OL,12,Fthey had plans for the rest of their
OL,13,Flives.
OL,15,F"Our lives will never be the same
OL,16,Fagain, she will always be in our
OL,17,Fhearts."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
