PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777050358
OL,3,CFamily left 'empty' after baby's death
OL,4,Cin suspected dog attack
OL,6,FThree people - two men aged 36 and 45
OL,7,Fand a 31-year-old woman - were
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of being in
OL,9,Fcharge of a dog that was dangerously
OL,10,Fout of control causing death.
OL,12,FThe woman was also arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of child neglect.
OL,15,FAll have been released on conditional
OL,16,Fbail.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
